episode: I've been excited about a new project I've been assigned to at work.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I've been feeling excited about a new project I was just assigned at work.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: What's the project about?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: We are standing up a new product line/segment at work and I'll be getting the online banking process and features defined.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Sounds like a big responsibility, you must be thrilled to lead it.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I am.  It's been quite a while since I worked on a new product launch.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: A chance to start fresh, that's probably energizing for you.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: It is.  It's a great opportunity to brush off some knowledge that I haven't applied in awhile.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Like riding a bike, it'll come back quickly, right?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I think so.  I feel really comfortable at work in general; good folks and lots of support to get things done.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That makes a huge difference, having a supportive team behind you.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: It took me many years and many jobs to get here.  I'd always worked for the big banks until a couple of years ago when I came out of an early retirement for this opportunity at a small regional bank.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: A fresh start at a smaller bank, that's a big change, how's the culture shift been?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Great.  I love being a bigger fish in a smaller pond.  My past experience and what got me ahead in my previous jobs is easy to apply here, and it makes me look like a genius.  I was rated "exceeds expectations" in my first annual review after only being here for about 6 months.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Nice validation, feels good to be recognized for your expertise, huh?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: It feels so good to be appreciated, and to see that every day I do something that actually makes a difference for our customers.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Making a tangible impact, that's very fulfilling.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: It is.  At a larger company what you "own" is so small it doesn't make as much of a difference as what I do here.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: You're making a dent, and that's satisfying.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: It is.  The only downside is the more I do, the more they expect me to do!  I am definitely overworked.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: The old "be careful what you wish for" syndrome!
